    " How do the functionality, research content generation, and usability of ChatGPT enable the development of investigative competencies in students?3) General objective To evaluate the impact of using ChatGPT on the development of investigative competencies in regular basic education students.",
    "4) Specific objectives To identify the scores of the control and experimental groups.",
    " To compare the scores between the control and experimental groups.",
    " To analyze the results regarding the investigative dimensions through the use of ChatGPT.",
    "C. Population and SampleThe study population consisted of 300 students from the High-Performance School of Arequipa, Peru."
